Prove 3.39

  p ⋀ true
=    〈 golden rule 〉
  p ≡ true ≡ p ⋁ true
=    〈 zero of ⋁ 〉
  p ≡ true ≡ true
=    〈 identity of ≡ 〉
  p ≡ true
=    〈 identity of ≡ 〉
  p ╱╱

