Prove 3.76.1

  p ⋀ q ⇒ p ⋁ r
=    〈 (3.59) 〉
  ¬(p ⋀ q) ⋁ p ⋁ r
=    〈 De Morgan 〉
  ¬p ⋁ ¬q ⋁ p ⋁ r
=    〈 symmetry of ≡, excluded middle 〉
  true ⋁ ¬q ⋁ r
=    〈 zero of ⋁ 〉
  true  ╱╱

