Prove 3.32

  p ⋁ q ≡ p ⋁ ¬q
=    〈 distributivity of ⋁ over ≡ 〉
  p ⋁ (q ≡ ¬q)
=    〈 (3.15) 〉
  p ⋁ false
=    〈 identity of ⋁ 〉
  p  ╱╱

