Prove 3.44b

  p ⋁ (¬p ⋀ q)
=    〈 golden rule 〉
  p ⋁ (¬p ≡ q ≡ ¬p ⋁ q)
=    〈 distributivity of ⋁ over ≡ 〉
  p ⋁ ¬p ≡ p ⋁ q ≡ p ⋁ ¬p ⋁ q
=    〈 excluded middle, twice 〉
  true ≡ p ⋁ q ≡ true ⋁ q
=    〈 zero of ⋁ 〉
  true ≡ p ⋁ q ≡ true
=    〈 identity of ≡, twice 〉
  p ⋁ q ╱╱

