Prove 3.44b

  p ⋁ (¬p ⋀ q)
=    〈 distributivity of ⋁ over ⋀ 〉
  (p ⋁ ¬p) ⋀ (p ⋁ q)
=    〈 excluded middle 〉
  true ⋀ (p ⋁ q)
=    〈 identity of ⋀ 〉
  p ⋁ q ╱╱
